    <h2 id="about">About</h2>

     <p>
        <strong>Pizza Time Pizza<code>&reg;</code></strong> has been proudly serving the Barrie area for over 
        <strong>17 years</strong>! What started as a small family-owned shop has grown into a local favorite, 
        known for our hand-tossed dough, homemade sauces, and generous toppings. We’re all about keeping things 
        <em>fresh, fast,</em> and <i><strong>flavorful</i></strong> — using only the highest quality ingredients sourced from 
        our trusted <a href="www.testlink.com">local suppliers.</a>
    </p>


